<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 11 Apr 2024 12:20:26 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>大众汽车将投资27亿美元在中国生产基地</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/volkswagen-invest-27-billion-chinese-production-site-2024-04-11/</link><description>大众汽车周四宣布，计划在中国投资 25 亿欧元（26.8 亿美元），扩建其位于安徽省合肥市的生产和创新中心。</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Apr 2024 11:35:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/volkswagen-invest-27-billion-chinese-production-site-2024-04-11/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：市场因美联储消除疑虑而动摇，欧洲央行下一步上涨</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-04-11/</link><description>迈克·多兰 (Mike Dolan) 对美国和全球市场未来一天的展望</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Apr 2024 10:04:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-04-11/</guid></item><item><title>评级下调和政府调查后万科股价、债券下跌</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/china-vanke-shares-bonds-fall-after-rating-cut-government-probe-2024-04-11/</link><description>在标准普尔取消其投资级地位以及该开发商证实一名高管正在接受调查的报道后，万科的股价和美元债券周四下跌，加剧了陷入困境的房地产行业的困境。</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Apr 2024 09:37:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/china-vanke-shares-bonds-fall-after-rating-cut-government-probe-2024-04-11/</guid></item><item><title>拜登将在菲律宾-日本峰会上对北京在南海的举动发出警告</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/biden-warn-beijings-south-china-sea-moves-philippines-japan-summit-2024-04-11/</link><description>随着美国、日本和菲律宾领导人齐聚白宫，反击北京在有争议的南海问题上对马尼拉加大施压，周四，中国与其邻国之间长期存在的紧张关系将成为人们关注的焦点。</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Apr 2024 09:09:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/biden-warn-beijings-south-china-sea-moves-philippines-japan-summit-2024-04-11/</guid></item><item><title>选举失败后，妥协可能会更好地服务好斗的韩国总统</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/after-election-rout-compromise-may-better-serve-south-koreas-combative-president-2024-04-11/</link><description>在通过不妥协、有时甚至是好斗的政治上台后，韩国总统尹锡烈如果希望在选举惨败后保护自己的遗产和政党，他可能不得不重新考虑他的标志性风格。</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Apr 2024 07:57:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/after-election-rout-compromise-may-better-serve-south-koreas-combative-president-2024-04-11/</guid></item><item><title>3月份中国出口可能重回收缩状态</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-exports-likely-swung-back-contraction-march-2024-04-11/</link><description>路透周四的一项民意调查显示，中国的出口在今年前两个月的增长好于预期后，3月份可能会出现下降，凸显了世界第二大经济体的复苏不平衡。</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Apr 2024 07:31:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-exports-likely-swung-back-contraction-march-2024-04-11/</guid></item><item><title>中国第一季度GDP增速将放缓至4.6%，加大刺激力度仍面临压力 - 路透调查</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-q1-gdp-growth-set-slow-46-keeps-pressure-more-stimulus-2024-04-11/</link><description>路透周四的一项民意调查显示，尽管有初步企稳迹象，中国第一季度经济可能较上年同期增长 4.6%，为一年来最慢增速，这给政策制定者带来了出台更多刺激措施的压力。</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Apr 2024 06:48:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-q1-gdp-growth-set-slow-46-keeps-pressure-more-stimulus-2024-04-11/</guid></item><item><title>优衣库运营商在第二季度利润低于预期后对欧洲和北美持乐观态度</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/uniqlo-operator-fast-retailing-says-q2-profit-rose-72-2024-04-11/</link><description>日本迅销公司(Fast Retailing Co)周四重申其利润将连续第三年创纪录的预测，优衣库所有者加大了在北美和欧洲的扩张力度，以与根深蒂固的竞争对手H&amp;amp;M和Zara所有者Inditex展开竞争。</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Apr 2024 06:22:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/uniqlo-operator-fast-retailing-says-q2-profit-rose-72-2024-04-11/</guid></item><item><title>《南华早报》称，中国总理李克强将于六月访问澳大利亚</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/chinese-premier-li-visit-australia-june-scmp-says-2024-04-11/</link><description>《南华早报》周四称，中国总理李强将于六月访问澳大利亚，这是两国关系解冻的最新一步。</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Apr 2024 06:14:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/chinese-premier-li-visit-australia-june-scmp-says-2024-04-11/</guid></item><item><title>前总统会见习近平后表示，台湾和中国可以解决分歧</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-china-can-resolve-differences-ex-president-says-after-meeting-xi-2024-04-11/</link><description>台湾前总统马英九周四在会见中国国家主席习近平后表示，台湾和中国可以和平解决分歧，并补充说，台湾海峡两岸人民拥有相同的文化和历史。</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Apr 2024 05:05:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-china-can-resolve-differences-ex-president-says-after-meeting-xi-2024-04-11/</guid></item><item><title>平安信托以中国房地产市场困境为由推迟还款</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/ping-an-trust-delays-repayment-citing-china-property-market-woes-2024-04-11/</link><description>中国平安保险的一家子公司未能按时偿还约1.07亿美元的信托产品，理由是房地产市场危机，并补充说它正在起诉投资该笔款项的开发商正荣地产。</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Apr 2024 04:06:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/ping-an-trust-delays-repayment-citing-china-property-market-woes-2024-04-11/</guid></item><item><title>随着河流水位进一步上涨，俄罗斯和哈萨克斯坦正在与创纪录的洪水作斗争</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/water-levels-rise-russian-rivers-flooding-zone-2024-04-11/</link><description>周四，俄罗斯城市奥伦堡遭遇水位上涨，俄罗斯和哈萨克斯坦的主要河流在该地区遭遇近一个世纪以来最严重的洪水决堤。</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Apr 2024 03:49:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/water-levels-rise-russian-rivers-flooding-zone-2024-04-11/</guid></item><item><title>美国将在贸易制裁决定中考虑对中国英国公司的担忧</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/us-consider-concerns-about-chinas-brite-trade-sanction-decisions-2024-04-11/</link><description>美国商务部表示，拜登政府在决定将哪些公司添加到贸易制裁名单时，将考虑共和党参议员马可·卢比奥提出的对中国芯片设计公司灿芯半导体的担忧。</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Apr 2024 02:39:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/us-consider-concerns-about-chinas-brite-trade-sanction-decisions-2024-04-11/</guid></item><item><title>美国通胀恐慌后欧洲转向欧洲央行</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-04-11/</link><description>在美国顽固的通胀数据引发数月来最严重的全球市场抛售并导致日元跌至34年低点后，交易员们正准备迎接周四动荡的欧洲央行会议。</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Apr 2024 02:15:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-04-11/</guid></item><item><title>中国疲软的CPI和工厂通货紧缩预示着更多刺激措施</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-consumer-prices-rise-2nd-month-factory-deflation-persists-2024-04-11/</link><description>3月份中国消费者通胀降温幅度超出预期，而生产者价格通缩持续存在，在需求依然疲软的情况下，政策制定者面临着推出更多刺激措施的压力。</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Apr 2024 01:43:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-consumer-prices-rise-2nd-month-factory-deflation-persists-2024-04-11/</guid></item></channel></rss>